title: Buffy S9: Love vs Life (from DHP 25-27|2013|Digital-1680|Empire)
description:
"Buffy the Vampire Slayer: Season 9" Special Issue, serialized in "Dark Horse Presents" issues 25 thru 27, compiled from Son of Ultron's releases thereof.

Starring Billy et al and Anaheed.
                                    Special-Guest-Starring The Primitive.

NOTE: This is likely going to be re-published as a one-shot by Dark Horse in short order, and subsequently released as a proper 0-Day item - no need to wait, though! :)
